Zero point energy                ...      0.48419995 Eh     303.84 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.03873865 Eh      24.31 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
Thermal translational correction ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Total thermal energy                  -3325.87759941 Eh


